@startuml

!include ../theme.puml

title RecallRadar - Leak Score Calculation

participant "RetentionScheduler"
participant "LeakScoreService"
participant "RevisionLogRepository"
participant "TopicMetricsRepository"

RetentionScheduler -> LeakScoreService : calculateScores()

LeakScoreService -> RevisionLogRepository : fetchRevisionHistory()

RevisionLogRepository --> LeakScoreService : Revision Logs

LeakScoreService -> LeakScoreService : Calculate Leak Score

LeakScoreService -> TopicMetricsRepository : saveMetrics()

TopicMetricsRepository --> LeakScoreService : Saved

note right

Initial Formula (MVP)

Leak Score =

DaysSinceLastRevision
× DifficultyWeight

-
RevisionCountBonus

Where:

Easy   = 1.0
Medium = 1.5
Hard   = 2.0

RevisionCountBonus =
TotalRevisions × 2

Higher Score =
Higher Risk Of Forgetting

end note

@enduml